track_notes:
classific EE  but you need HELMET for more safety.

Rise by direct way ( there is NOT path but is the best choise )

Descent by long way ( only some part of path and a lot a rocks ) only if you have spare time and good weather so You can appreciate the view

Depending from were you park, you can make it shorter. To reach the summit, the WX must be good, if rain it could be dangerous, if more than one climber, a helmet is welcome. The sloope is very hard, a pair of walk stick, and good shoes needed. there is some GSM network on summit witch is not very large for a large dipole.
2023 in my birthday anniversary, alone. About 3 H of rise.
track_title: class EE  rocky HELMET required x safety Phone OK
